eligibility.inclusivecriteria:
For more information regarding BMS clinical trial participation, please visit www.BMSStudyConnect.com.
- Chronic Hepatitis C, Genotype 1
- HCV RNA >100,000 IU/mL at screening;
- Seronegative for Human immunodeficiency virus (HIV) and Hepatitis B surface antigen (HBsAg);
- Liver biopsy within prior 2 years; subjects with compensated cirrhosis can enroll and will be capped at approximately 10%

eligibility.exclusivecriteria:
-  Any evidence of liver disease other than HCV;

          -  Co-infection with HIV;

          -  Diagnosed or suspected hepatocellular carcinoma;

          -  Medical history or laboratory value abnormalities that would prohibit the use of
             Pegylated Interferon Alpha-2a or Ribavirin
